Albert LANE, Appellant, v. FITZSIMMONS STORES, Limited, and Thriftimart Stores, Appellees. SAME v. VAN’S MARKETS, a Corporation, Appellee. SAME v. GREAT ATLANTIC & PACIFIC TEA COMPANY, a Corporation, Appellee. No. 11202. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Jan. 13, 1948. Albert Lane, in pro, per. for appellant. Mitchell, Johnson & Bates, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellees.

*215Before MATHEWS, STEPHENS, and ORR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

These appeals are dismissed for want of prosecution.
